# Closed-Loop Monitoring (ADR-006 / ADR-007 / ADR-008)

Mirror of `.windsurf/rules/13-closed-loop-monitoring.md`. Full rationale
and detailed invariants live there and in AGENTS.md.

## Non-negotiable invariants

### D-20 — Identity + lineage on every prediction
- Every logged prediction MUST carry `prediction_id` (UUID) and `entity_id`
  (stable business key). `model_version` MUST be present.
- `PredictionRequest` MUST require `entity_id`.
- `PredictionResponse` MUST return `prediction_id` for client correlation.
- Never synthesize `entity_id` from features — it must be a stable key.

### D-21 — Fire-and-forget logging (no handler blocking)
- `log_prediction()` MUST return after enqueue. No sync network I/O on
  the hot path.
- Backends run via `run_in_executor(None, backend.write_batch, ...)` —
  same rationale as D-03 for inference.
- Buffer MUST drain on FastAPI lifespan shutdown (`await close()`).

### D-22 — Observability failures never break serving
- `log_prediction()` MUST swallow exceptions; errors increment
  `prediction_log_errors_total` but never propagate.
- Alert on `rate(prediction_log_errors_total[15m]) / rate(prediction_log_total[15m]) > 0.05`
  rather than via HTTP 5xx.

## Slicing contract (ADR-007)
- `slice_values` dict keys MUST match names in `configs/slices.yaml`.
- Cardinality bounded — unbounded free-text slices are FORBIDDEN.
- Below `min_samples_per_slice`, mark the slice `insufficient_data`.

## Ground-truth contract (ADR-006)
- `fetch_labels_from_source()` is a USER stub; CSV is dev-only.
- Rows: non-null entity_id, true_value; `label_ts` = moment the label became known.
- JOIN causality: `label_ts >= prediction_ts`.

## Champion/Challenger contract (ADR-008)
- C/C is STOP-class governance. Only promoted via CI with step summary.
- Both McNemar p-value AND bootstrap ΔAUC CI MUST align.
- Tri-state decision: promote / keep / block. Margin changes require ADR.

## Agent behavior by file

| File pattern | Mode |
|--------------|------|
| `app/fastapi_app.py`, `app/main.py` | AUTO (preserve D-21/D-22) |
| `prediction_logger.py` | CONSULT (affects all services) |
| `champion_challenger.py`, `configs/champion_challenger.yaml` | STOP (governance) |

See AGENTS.md for the full Anti-Patterns table D-01 → D-22.
